Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
On behalf of the GPT Group, CBRE & Colliers are pleased to present For Lease Site 3 & 4 in the successful Wembley Business Park (www.wembleybusinesspark.com.au). 

Located only 30min from the Brisbane Port and Airport, 25 mins from the Brisbane CBD and situated on the Logan Motorway the estate offers unrivalled arterial access. 

There are two remaining site options after successful Stage 1 & 2 developments for DHL and JB Hi-fi. 
Site 3 & 4: 
•	Site 3: Flexible design accommodating tenancies from 7,000sqm* to 20,000sqm +*
•	Site 4: Tenancies from 4,000sqm* to 16,000sqm*
•	Open plan A-grade offices with amenities 
•	DA Approved and ready for Pre-Lease 
•	Multiple driveway crossovers for efficient traffic management 
•	7t* post load to warehouse slab and 13.7 metre* warehouse ridge height
•	15 metre* all-weather awning for hardstand loading
•	36m* hardstand depths 
•	Recessed loading docks with levellers  
•	Separate access and car parking for staff/visitors
•	Approved for B-Double access and 24/7 operation
•	Can be delivered within 9mths* from commitment  
•	ESFR fire sprinkler system
•	LED lighting throughout and water re-use
•	Close proximity to amenity (Shops, food, bus & train)
•	Competitive financial packages on offer  
*Approx. 

With over 50% of the development now committed, we welcome the opportunity to discuss your requirement within one of the Logan Motorway’s most prestigious logistics business parks. 

Contact the agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: HIGH PROFILE LOGISTICS ESTATE – LAST TWO SITES REMAINING IN WEMBLEY BUSINESS PARK

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
On behalf of Charter Hall, CBRE & Knight Frank are pleased to present For Lease the latest release in the successful Motorway Industrial Park, Berrinba.  

Located only 30 minutes from the Brisbane Port and Airport, 25 minutes from the Brisbane CBD and situated on the Logan Motorway with access via the recently upgraded Wembley Road interchange.  

After the recent completion of warehouses for Mitre 10 and QLS Logistics there are three remaining stages offering the following: 
•	Flexible designs accommodating tenancies from 11,000sqm* to 24,800sqm +*
•	Stage 1 – Building 3: 11,300sqm* 
•	Stage 1 - Building 4: 16,500sqm*
•	Stage 2 – Building 5: 12,362sqm* – 24,802sqm*
•	Stage 3 – Building 6: 8,615sqm – 17,230sqm*     
•	Open plan, A-grade offices and amenities 
•	Multiple driveway crossovers and separate access for staff/ visitors  
•	Minimum 10.5m* springing height – 13.7m* ridge height.  
•	Up to 39m* all-weather awning for hardstand loading & 42m* hardstand depths 
•	Recessed loading docks with levellers (if required) 
•	ESFR fire suppression systems  
•	Excellent Motorway exposure for signage opportunities 
•	Early site works now complete
*Approx.

Berrinba is an established, prime industrial and logistics hub within South East Queensland. It’s a preferred location for interstate distribution given proximity to major transport routes and manufacturing users for its ability to draw on a skilled, local workforce.     

Contact the agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.

•	403sqm* industrial office/warehouse 
•	Exclusive complex of only 6 units 
•	114sqm* of first grade office accommodation
•	289sqm* of 8m high warehouse 
•	Solar Panels and LED high bay lighting 
•	Unrivalled access to Gateway and Logan Motorway
*Approx.

Located at the entry/ exit point from the Logan Motorway is this exclusive and well-designed industrial complex. Comprising of only 5 units, the estate has ample room for parking, hardstand and container loading. Please contact the exclusive agents, CBRE for further information or an inspection.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: ONE OF THE BEST ON LOGAN MOTORWAY!
